{"tid":940397,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[車迷高質]車仔發聲明譴責反閃族球迷","createTime":"2018-12-14T02:05:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-14T07:53:35.000Z","uid":31626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e6d0ecdaee366a51af668636e1fba98eedf5adba","tid":940397,"uid":31626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T02:05:06.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=Xm7WKmrItRA9qTfGUjZ%2FawKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=0a8affcc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】部份車路士球迷在歐霸盃分組賽大叫反閃族的口號，遭會方發表聲明譴責。<br />\n<br />\n車路士球迷大概是全英國其中最不聽話的球迷，上次對曼城的種族辱罵史達寧的風波未平，周四歐霸盃分組賽作客2:2和匈牙利的維迪奧頓，又鬧出球迷高呼反閃族口號的事件，恐怕又難逃歐洲足協的處罰，會方賽後也馬上發表聲明譴責。<br />\n<br />\n聲明寫道：「反閃族以及一切不尊重種族、宗教的行為，都違反球會和大部份車路士球迷的價值觀。我們不容許這樣的球迷存在。我們從班主、董事局、教練、球員，都大聲疾呼反對這樣的做法！我們將嚴懲這樣的球迷。」<br />\n<br />\n車仔確做了該做的事，今年1月還舉行活動，教育球迷要捨棄反閃族的做法，可惜部份球迷依然重犯，實在令球會萬分無奈。"},{"pid":"2af943dc3a9fbdaebd70be076104029f8ab70e90","tid":940397,"uid":31626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T02:07:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c373ef572cbf13c68d3f6e213a485bfda5793908","tid":940397,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T02:08:48.000Z","msg":"反閃點解？"},{"pid":"aacd26c5f2c83c423f8da2cabf3cebcc11e6a14e","tid":940397,"uid":31626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c373ef572cbf13c68d3f6e213a485bfda5793908","tid":940397,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T02:08:48.000Z","msg":"反閃點解？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T02:10:47.000Z","msg":"反猶太"},{"pid":"de833a0b6ba0ecff338db0aad60feba039b864ef","tid":940397,"uid":35648,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c373ef572cbf13c68d3f6e213a485bfda5793908","tid":940397,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T02:08:48.000Z","msg":"反閃點解？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T02:11:29.000Z"